  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Provide Clean Water for a School in Gilgil, Kenya</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will provide the Morop Mixed Day Secondary School with a new 10,000 liter water tank that will supply clean and safe water to the children and the surrounding community.  This will increase the retention of students in school.  Having clean water reduces student absence due to infection from water borne diseases.  With clean water, the school can implement a tree planting program as well as kitchen gardens which can augment the lunch program.</narrative>
  </description>
